{
  "stem": "11274.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I make sure that he brings you telephone booths.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He brought me the telephone booths, he called Florynka, got the post office-- because in all those villages, there was a telephone in the post office.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was it, nobody had telephones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Called Florynka, the post office.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he got connected, he said, this is a German officer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I like to speak to the chief of the-- the head of the post office.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he said, here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You talking to her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm going to give you a person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, I want you to give her an honest answer, he said to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, I'm Rena Kornreich and I-- in Florynka, this and this house-- I remembered the name of the farmer-- are living my parents, and I would like to speak to one of them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could you send somebody?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can wait on the telephone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even though it's expensive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said you can wait.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And send a messenger to get him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We waited about five minutes or 10 minutes, and the, the man on the other side of the telephone in Poland says, the messenger came back and said, in this house is only such and such family-- the owners of it-- and there is no Jewish family there.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they don't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was the last time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't-- this time I didn't get contact with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found out later after the war from Alex-- because all the people that left Tylicz were sort of in the same towns or near it-- that were taken all-- probably before, before Passover-- taken to a ghetto in Nowy Sacz somewhere, or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He doesn't know for sure either because he escaped to Czechoslovakia too.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
